title: HTS 8504
text: Electrical transformers, static converters (for example, rectifiers) and inductors.

title: HTS 8536
text: Electrical apparatus for switching or protecting electrical circuits, or for making connections to or in electrical circuits.

title: HTS 8544
text: Insulated (including enameled or anodized) wire, cable (including coaxial cable) and other insulated electric conductors, whether or not fitted with connectors.

title: HTS 8517
text: Telephone sets, including smartphones, and other apparatus for the transmission or reception of voice, images or other data.
